chapter:

        Virtuoso
            Functions Guide & Reference



The Virtuoso SQL Functions Guide contains reference manual entries for
                built-in SQL functions and procedures.


The Virtuoso XPATH & XQUERY Functions Guide contains reference manual entries of the
                built-in functions of the Virtuoso XPATH Processor. These can be used in XPATH, XSLT, XQuery.




